<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Seoyeon Tour</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif; }
        .hero { height:100vh; display:flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; text-align: center; }
        .nav-link { color: #555 !important; font-size: 0.9rem; }
        .nav-link:hover { color: #000 !important; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg bg-white shadow-sm fixed-top px-4">
        <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold tracking-wide" href="/">SEOYEON TOUR</a>
        <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navMenu">
            <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navMenu">
            <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto gap-2">
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/introduce">소개</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/event">이벤트</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/honeymoon-europe">허니문-유럽</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/honeymoon-resort">허니문-휴양지</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/group">단체여행</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/package">패키지</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/reviews">후기</a></li>
                <% if (user) { %>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link fw-bold text-dark" href="/mypage"><%= user.name %>님</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/mypage">마이페이지</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link text-danger" href="/auth/logout">로그아웃</a>
                    </li>
                <% } else { %>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/login">로그인</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link text-primary fw-bold" href="/signup-page">회원가입</a>
                    </li>
                <% } %>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div id="heroCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="false">
        <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img src="/images/paris.jpg" class="d-block w-100" style="height:100vh; object-fit:cover;" alt="파리">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-flex flex-column justify-content-center" style="top:0; bottom:0;">
                    <h1 class="display-3 fw-bold">SEOYEON TOUR</h1>
                    <h2 class="fw-normal">아름다운 인연의 시작</h2>
                    <p>돌아오시는 그날까지 서연투어가 함께 합니다</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="/images/venice.jpg" class="d-block w-100" style="height:100vh; object-fit:cover;" alt="베니스">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-flex flex-column justify-content-center" style="top:0; bottom:0;">
                    <h1 class="display-3 fw-bold">SEOYEON TOUR</h1>
                    <h2 class="fw-normal">아름다운 인연의 시작</h2>
                    <p>돌아오시는 그날까지 서연투어가 함께 합니다</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="/images/maldives.jpg" class="d-block w-100" style="height:100vh; object-fit:cover;" alt="몰디브">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-flex flex-column justify-content-center" style="top:0; bottom:0;">
                    <h1 class="display-3 fw-bold">SEOYEON TOUR</h1>
                    <h2 class="fw-normal">아름다운 인연의 시작</h2>
                    <p>돌아오시는 그날까지 서연투어가 함께 합니다</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#heroCarousel" data-bs-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon"></span>
        </button>
        <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#heroCarousel" data-bs-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon"></span>
        </button>
    </div>

    <section class="py-5 bg-light">
        <div class="container py-5">
            <p class="text-center text-muted small mb-1">PRODUCTS</p>
            <h2 class="text-center fw-light mb-5">여행 상품</h2>
            <div class="row g-4">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm h-100 p-4">
                        <p class="text-muted small">HONEYMOON</p>
                        <h5 class="fw-medium">허니문</h5>
                        <p class="text-muted small">유럽, 몰디브, 발리 등<br>특별한 허니문 여행</p>
                        <a href="/honeymoon-europe" class="text-dark small">자세히 보기 →</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm h-100 p-4">
                        <p class="text-muted small">PACKAGE</p>
                        <h5 class="fw-medium">패키지</h5>
                        <p class="text-muted small">알차게 구성된<br>패키지 여행 상품</p>
                        <a href="/package" class="text-dark small">자세히 보기 →</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm h-100 p-4">
                        <p class="text-muted small">GROUP</p>
                        <h5 class="fw-medium">단체여행</h5>
                        <p class="text-muted small">기업·학교·동호회<br>단체 맞춤 여행</p>
                        <a href="/group" class="text-dark small">자세히 보기 →</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="py-5 text-center text-muted small border-top">
        <p class="fw-medium text-dark mb-1">SEOYEON TOUR</p>
        <p>대표자: 원서연, 정유진</p>
        <p>Tel: 010-2987-7368 · Email: angelo2001@naver.com</p>
        <p class="mt-3">© 2025 Seoyeon Tour. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
